{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/steam_crop_title_main.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A TWISTED PLACE is a 2.5D Single-Player Horror game with multiple chapters that alternates between Side-view and 1st person gameplay for a scarier experience. Find your way through a nightmare unlike anything you've ever experienced before. In this unconventional horror game you'll have to survive as best as you can while being surrounded by horrors beyond human comprehension. Interact with the environment to solve puzzles and to find tools, information and secrets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/text_oct_hide.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You're constantly hunted by cursed entities that lurk in the darkness. Your only option is to run and hide before you get caught, whether it\u2019s hiding under a bed, slipping into a closet, or crouching behind debris, the environment becomes your lifeline.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/new_woman_gif.gif?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/Paragraph_separator.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/text_oct_inspect.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll need to explore and interact with your surroundings to find tools and gather information needed to progress. Every room, drawer, and hidden corner could hold something important. Along the way you can also discover secrets and collectibles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/gif_2_store.gif?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/Paragraph_separator.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/text_oct_escape.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your ultimate goal is to escape from the twisted place that traps you. The horrors you encounter are relentless, and the only way to survive is to find a way out.<br>Can you make it out alive? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/tube_gif.gif?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/Paragraph_separator.png?t=1737162730\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/text_features.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Atmospheric Horror that alternates sideview and 1st person gameplay;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Single-Player;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1 hour and a half of game duration; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique &amp; Unconventional graphics with scary and eerie content; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple chapters &amp; hidden collectibles;  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interactive environment; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Disclaimer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game contains disturbing content.<br>Play it at your own risk.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2929020?t=1737162730","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1737162730","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/7767d7b09400210fd935b84f22122c5de30328b5/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737162730","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/7767d7b09400210fd935b84f22122c5de30328b5/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737162730","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"The game contains scary & disturbing content"},"demos":[{"appid":3260770,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/steam_crop_title_main.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A TWISTED PLACE is a 2.5D Single-Player Horror game with multiple chapters that alternates between Side-view and 1st person gameplay for a scarier experience. Find your way through a nightmare unlike anything you've ever experienced before. In this unconventional horror game you'll have to survive as best as you can while being surrounded by horrors beyond human comprehension. Interact with the environment to solve puzzles and to find tools, information and secrets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/text_oct_hide.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You're constantly hunted by cursed entities that lurk in the darkness. Your only option is to run and hide before you get caught, whether it\u2019s hiding under a bed, slipping into a closet, or crouching behind debris, the environment becomes your lifeline.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/new_woman_gif.gif?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/Paragraph_separator.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/text_oct_inspect.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll need to explore and interact with your surroundings to find tools and gather information needed to progress. Every room, drawer, and hidden corner could hold something important. Along the way you can also discover secrets and collectibles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/gif_2_store.gif?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/Paragraph_separator.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/text_oct_escape.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your ultimate goal is to escape from the twisted place that traps you. The horrors you encounter are relentless, and the only way to survive is to find a way out.<br>Can you make it out alive? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/tube_gif.gif?t=1737162730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/Paragraph_separator.png?t=1737162730\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/extras/text_features.png?t=1737162730\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Atmospheric Horror that alternates sideview and 1st person gameplay;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Single-Player;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1 hour and a half of game duration; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique &amp; Unconventional graphics with scary and eerie content; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple chapters &amp; hidden collectibles;  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interactive environment; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Disclaimer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game contains disturbing content.<br>Play it at your own risk.</p>","developers":["Wraithen Studio"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2929020/header.jpg?t=1737162730","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257083583,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257083583/movie480.mp4?t=1734626956","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257083583/movie_max.mp4?t=1734626956"},"name":"A Twisted Place - Teaser","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257083583/374d6dede7d303148e65a3fd0bddaeacb688e3b7/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1734626956","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257083583/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1734626956","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257083583/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1734626956"}},{"highlight":false,"id":257015423,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257015423/movie480.mp4?t=17311510